{"updated":1769695195,"is_labeled":false,"copyright_permission":"need_review","settings":{"table_of_contents":{"enabled":false}},"excerpt":"1. 架构设计建议从用户的使用习惯出发，对于国产AI芯片，不大建议自我开发一个与生态不兼容的集合通信库，费时费力还破坏用户的使用习惯与编程习惯。更建议基于NCCL进行移植，保持接口的一致性兼容集合通信库的调用方，比如pytorch, vLLM等。同时也使得一些厂家的自定义NCCL 插件可以无缝使用。 而自我开发一个集合通信库比较的耗费人力，成本较高，难以借力NCCL的生态，同时也难以兼容用户的自定义NCCL插件，对用户不大友好，维…","admin_closed_comment":false,"voting":0,"article_type":"normal","reason":"","force_login_when_click_read_more":false,"excerpt_title":"","id":"1971319954541348800","voteup_count":4,"title_image":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-0e2662d69e59d31913d175a8b2600136_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b","has_column":true,"url":"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1971319954541348800","comment_permission":"censor","author":{"is_followed":false,"avatar_url_template":"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-eb249fe9f1461ad37894b3362aa80eb4.jpg?source=d16d100b","uid":"1019697603679793152","user_type":"people","is_following":false,"type":"people","url_token":"changping123","id":"8ffff72080e204609981e6e00fe98684","description":"某Ai芯片公司架构师","name":"常平","is_advertiser":false,"headline":"为学，闻道，践行！","gender":1,"url":"/people/8ffff72080e204609981e6e00fe98684","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-eb249fe9f1461ad37894b3362aa80eb4_l.jpg?source=d16d100b","is_org":false,"badge":[]},"comment_count":0,"created":1762781291,"content":"<h3>1. 架构设计建议</h3><p data-pid=\"1YVmjLeN\">从用户的使用习惯出发，对于国产AI芯片，不大建议自我开发一个与生态不兼容的集合通信库，费时费力还破坏用户的使用习惯与编程习惯。更建议基于NCCL进行移植，保持接口的一致性兼容集合通信库的调用方，比如pytorch, vLLM等。同时也使得一些厂家的自定义NCCL 插件可以无缝使用。</p><p data-pid=\"i5XleUTG\">而自我开发一个集合通信库比较的耗费人力，成本较高，难以借力NCCL的生态，同时也难以兼容用户的自定义NCCL插件，对用户不大友好，维护成本也会非常高。</p><p data-pid=\"9GN7alIs\">简单来说，基于NCCL移植国产AI芯片的集合通信库，简单的版本只需要替换掉自定义算子以及NVLINK的通信接口，即可。这样可以快速拉起一个可运行的国产AI芯片的集合通信库，省时省力。后续再逐步补齐产品化相关特性。</p><h3>1.1 NCCL核心架构层次</h3><p data-pid=\"aplxGWhC\">NCCL的架构可以分解为以下几个关键层次：</p><h3><b>第1层：设备抽象层</b></h3><ul><li data-pid=\"zvQT9iPR\"><b>核心文件</b>: <code>src/include/device.h</code>, <code>src/device/common.h</code></li><li data-pid=\"EyyfGKxl\"><b>功能职责</b>:</li><li data-pid=\"sZ_OuF-8\">线程层次结构（Warp/Block/Grid）</li><li data-pid=\"OXBQI2wr\">共享内存管理</li><li data-pid=\"cOA3orVZ\">同步原语（Barrier、Atomic操作）</li><li data-pid=\"wZrpwwkS\"> 内存一致性模型<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"nY6wsbXn\"><b>CUDA依赖度</b>:  极高，国产AI芯片在在硬件设计上如果没考虑到这一点，那么移植起来会比较的痛苦。<br/> </li></ul><h3><b>第2层：传输层</b></h3><ul><li data-pid=\"GuY-fGR5\"><b>核心文件</b>: <code>src/transport/</code>目录</li><li data-pid=\"iQiqIbFg\"><code>p2p.cc</code> - GPU间点对点通信</li><li data-pid=\"w3nhMLV0\"><code>shm.cc</code> - 共享内存传输</li><li data-pid=\"dMwqHc13\"><code>net.cc</code>, <code>net_ib.cc</code> - 网络传输（InfiniBand、Socket）</li><li data-pid=\"6KPIx9gR\"><code>nvls.cc</code> - NVLink Sharp支持</li><li data-pid=\"UmWVdFFh\"><code>coll_net.cc</code> - 集合网络操作</li><li data-pid=\"kQvhXLXn\"><b>CUDA依赖度</b>:  高（主要在IPC和RDMA），国产AI芯片可以把NVLINK 替换成自定义的通信协议。同时Coll_net 如果难以支持 也是可以不支持的，非必须。</li></ul><h3><b>第3层：拓扑发现与调度</b></h3><ul><li data-pid=\"9EWhXeWA\"><b>核心文件</b>: <code>src/graph/topo.cc</code>, <code>src/graph/topo.h</code></li><li data-pid=\"WpXRT4cG\"><b>功能职责</b>:</li><li data-pid=\"8j4mzE9m\">系统拓扑检测</li><li data-pid=\"eY582PQR\">带宽/延迟性能建模</li><li data-pid=\"2mKYb1-K\">最优路径计算</li><li data-pid=\"POdh4WJT\">算法选择与调优</li><li data-pid=\"95GAAX93\"><b>CUDA依赖度</b>:  中等（主要是NVML API），这一层国产AI芯片甚至可以不支持XXML API也是可以移植的。</li></ul><h3><b>第4层：设备端内核</b></h3><ul><li data-pid=\"9MOrPNm4\"><b>核心文件</b>: <code>src/device/</code>目录<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"oIvEPgsy\"><code>primitives.h</code> - 通信原语基类<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"dgDdO9yZ\"><code>prims_simple.h</code>, <code>prims_ll.h</code>, <code>prims_ll128.h</code> - 协议实现</li><li data-pid=\"bdMaWx-o\"><code>all_reduce.h</code>, <code>all_gather.h</code>, <code>reduce_scatter.h</code> - 集合算法</li><li data-pid=\"WIIzRe2C\"><code>common_kernel.h</code> - 内核通用功能<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"W0_Wlio-\"><b>CUDA依赖度</b>: 极高，这一层对国产AI芯片移植起来会比较的痛苦，都是自定义算子，也需要硬件能支持。<br/> </li></ul><h3>1.2 关键数据结构</h3><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"c1\">// 设备通信结构（src/include/device.h）\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span><span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"n\">ncclDevChannel</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"n\">ncclDevChannelPeer</span><span class=\"o\">**</span> <span class=\"n\">peers</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>  <span class=\"c1\">// 对等节点信息\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>  <span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"n\">ncclRing</span> <span class=\"n\">ring</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>                <span class=\"c1\">// Ring算法拓扑\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>  <span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"n\">ncclTree</span> <span class=\"n\">tree</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>                <span class=\"c1\">// Tree算法拓扑\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>  <span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"n\">ncclNvls</span> <span class=\"n\">nvls</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>                <span class=\"c1\">// NVLink Sharp拓扑\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>  <span class=\"n\">uint32_t</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">workFifoDone</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>              <span class=\"c1\">// 工作完成计数器\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>  <span class=\"n\">uint64_t</span> <span class=\"n\">workCounter</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>                <span class=\"c1\">// 工作计数器\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span><span class=\"p\">};</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">// 连接信息（src/include/device.h）\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span><span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"n\">ncclConnInfo</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"kt\">char</span> <span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">buffs</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">NCCL_NUM_PROTOCOLS</span><span class=\"p\">];</span>    <span class=\"c1\">// 通信缓冲区\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>  <span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">mhandles</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">NCCL_NUM_PROTOCOLS</span><span class=\"p\">];</span>  <span class=\"c1\">// 内存句柄\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>  <span class=\"n\">uint64_t</span> <span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">tail</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>                      <span class=\"c1\">// 队列尾指针\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>  <span class=\"n\">uint64_t</span> <span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">head</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>                      <span class=\"c1\">// 队列头指针\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>  <span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">flags</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>                           <span class=\"c1\">// 直接通信标志\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>  <span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">stepSize</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>                        <span class=\"c1\">// 步长大小\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span><span class=\"p\">};</span></code></pre></div><h3>1.3 协议机制</h3><p data-pid=\"aAiYEU5n\">NCCL支持三种传输协议：</p><ol><li data-pid=\"N0xsPril\"><b>Simple协议</b>: 批量传输，高吞吐</li><li data-pid=\"mdG4Js88\"><b>LL (Low Latency)协议</b>: 低延迟，适合小消息</li><li data-pid=\"C8CwHUH0\"><b>LL128协议</b>: 128字节行，平衡性能</li></ol><h3>2. 移植工作分解</h3><h3>2.1 第一阶段：硬件抽象层（HAL）构建 - 关键优先级</h3><p data-pid=\"ZXrL8QiH\">这一层如果runtime api 已经兼容CUDA Runtime API ，那么移植起来会比较的顺利。</p><h3><b>任务2.1.1: CUDA Runtime API替换</b></h3><p data-pid=\"2_qEqGeI\"><b>需要创建的抽象层</b>:</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"c1\">// 建议的HAL接口设计\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span><span class=\"k\">typedef</span> <span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"c1\">// 设备管理\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>  <span class=\"n\">ncclResult_t</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">getDeviceCount</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"kt\">int</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">count</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">ncclResult_t</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">setDevice</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">device</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">ncclResult_t</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">getDevice</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"kt\">int</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">device</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n\n  <span class=\"c1\">// 内存管理\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>  <span class=\"n\">ncclResult_t</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">malloc</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">**</span> <span class=\"n\">ptr</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">size_t</span> <span class=\"n\">size</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">ncclResult_t</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">free</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">ptr</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">ncclResult_t</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">hostMalloc</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">**</span> <span class=\"n\">ptr</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">size_t</span> <span class=\"n\">size</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">ncclResult_t</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">memcpy</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">dst</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"k\">const</span> <span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">src</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">size_t</span> <span class=\"n\">size</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">kind</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">ncclResult_t</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">memcpyAsync</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">dst</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"k\">const</span> <span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">src</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">size_t</span> <span class=\"n\">size</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">kind</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">stream</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n\n  <span class=\"c1\">// 流管理\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>  <span class=\"n\">ncclResult_t</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">streamCreate</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">**</span> <span class=\"n\">stream</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">ncclResult_t</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">streamDestroy</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">stream</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">ncclResult_t</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">streamSynchronize</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">stream</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n\n  <span class=\"c1\">// 事件管理\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>  <span class=\"n\">ncclResult_t</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">eventCreate</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">**</span> <span class=\"n\">event</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">ncclResult_t</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">eventRecord</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">event</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">stream</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">ncclResult_t</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">eventSynchronize</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">event</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span> <span class=\"n\">ncclDeviceOps_t</span><span class=\"p\">;</span></code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"i3Rdi4Ck\"><b>需要修改的文件</b>（示例）:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"Thf7ABVh\"><code>src/init.cc</code> - 初始化流程</li><li data-pid=\"eheMuW2p\"><code>src/transport/p2p.cc</code> - P2P通信</li><li data-pid=\"hzngOU4h\"><code>src/proxy.cc</code> - 代理线程</li><li data-pid=\"OdsqBh5i\">所有包含<code>cudaMalloc</code>、<code>cudaMemcpy</code>等调用的文件</li></ul><h3><b>任务2.1.2: CUDA kernel移植</b></h3><p data-pid=\"-qPSQe6u\">这一层需要写自定义算子，工作量比较的大，同时也依赖于硬件的支持。</p><p data-pid=\"GZyn-LZ1\"><b>核心挑战</b>:</p><p data-pid=\"XqdSetYs\"> 1，<b>线程模型映射</b><br/> </p><ul><li data-pid=\"eXrHJdyD\"> CUDA Warp (32线程) → NPU芯片的SIMD单元</li><li data-pid=\"qCajIuxd\"> CUDA Block → NPU芯片的工作组</li><li data-pid=\"0cuNM5qn\"> CUDA Grid → NPU芯片的任务调度<br/> </li></ul><p data-pid=\"uPdpL02l\"> 2，<b>共享内存模型</b><br/> </p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">// NCCL当前使用方式（src/device/common.h）\n   extern __shared__ ncclShmemData ncclShmem;\n   extern __shared__ ulong2 ncclShmemPerWarp[];\n\n   // 需要映射到您芯片的共享内存机制</code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"aH69eCTU\"><b>3，同步原语替换</b></p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">   // CUDA同步（src/device/common.h）\n   __device__ inline void barrier_sync(int name, int nThreads) {\n     asm volatile(&#34;barrier.sync.aligned %0, %1;&#34; :: &#34;r&#34;(name), &#34;r&#34;(nThreads) : &#34;memory&#34;);\n   }\n\n   // 需要替换为NPU芯片的barrier指令</code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"3LtFoGcV\"><b>关键文件</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"-Wfa_fTh\"><code>src/device/common.cu</code> - 设备端通用代码</li><li data-pid=\"yc7bdiM4\"><code>src/device/primitives.h</code> - 通信原语</li><li data-pid=\"kO9nBuM3\"><code>src/device/all_reduce.h</code> - AllReduce算法</li><li data-pid=\"qm0dHSlk\"><code>src/device/reduce_kernel.h</code> - Reduce内核</li></ul><h3><b>任务2.1.3: 内存模型适配</b></h3><p data-pid=\"_SmJDEVr\"><b>需要适配的内存特性</b>:</p><p data-pid=\"MwYM_PLL\"> 1，<b>全局内存访问模式</b><br/> </p><ul><li data-pid=\"4t66pgnb\"> 合并访问（Coalesced Access）</li><li data-pid=\"FdmSTKPM\">缓存策略</li><li data-pid=\"mWUFOxPU\"> 内存对齐要求<br/> </li></ul><p data-pid=\"X9aXLb62\"> 2，<b>共享内存容量</b><br/> </p><ul><li data-pid=\"Shvg6UtA\"> NCCL假设: 每个Block至少64KB</li><li data-pid=\"6i1yGxsc\">动态共享内存分配</li><li data-pid=\"dwzvrzj5\"> Bank冲突避免<br/> </li></ul><p data-pid=\"R_iMM5aG\"> 3，<b>寄存器压力</b><br/> </p><ul><li data-pid=\"AYUavGjo\"> NCCL内核通常需要64-128个寄存器/线程</li><li data-pid=\"tSH437oZ\">需要调整内核以适应您芯片的寄存器文件大小</li></ul><h3>2.2 第二阶段：传输层适配</h3><h3><b>任务2.2.1: 点对点通信</b></h3><p data-pid=\"NptfPNkW\"><b>核心工作</b>:</p><p data-pid=\"HUWq2p-N\"><b>1，替换CUDA IPC机制</b>（<code>src/transport/p2p.cc</code>）</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"c1\">// 当前使用cudaIpcGetMemHandle/cudaIpcOpenMemHandle\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>   <span class=\"c1\">// 需要实现您芯片的进程间内存共享机制\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>   <span class=\"n\">ncclResult_t</span> <span class=\"nf\">chipIpcGetMemHandle</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">devPtr</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">chipIpcMemHandle_t</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">handle</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n   <span class=\"n\">ncclResult_t</span> <span class=\"nf\">chipIpcOpenMemHandle</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">**</span> <span class=\"n\">devPtr</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">chipIpcMemHandle_t</span> <span class=\"n\">handle</span><span class=\"p\">);</span></code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"bmTcBSpK\"> 2，<b>芯片间直连支持</b><br/> </p><ul><li data-pid=\"ZeZVqvke\"> 是否支持类似NVLink的高速互联？</li><li data-pid=\"WvHEZI0F\"> 带宽：建议≥200 GB/s双向</li><li data-pid=\"ljGt1JTP\"> 延迟：建议&lt;500ns<br/> </li></ul><p data-pid=\"xAMl7Wj8\">3，<b>P2P类型支持</b>（参考<code>src/transport/p2p.cc:17</code>）<br/> </p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"k\">enum</span> <span class=\"n\">p2pType</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span> \n     <span class=\"n\">P2P_DIRECT</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>       <span class=\"c1\">// 直接访问（需要芯片支持）\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>     <span class=\"n\">P2P_INTERMEDIATE</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"c1\">// 通过中间节点\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>     <span class=\"n\">P2P_IPC</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>          <span class=\"c1\">// 进程间通信\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>     <span class=\"n\">P2P_CUMEM</span>         <span class=\"c1\">// cuMem API（新特性）\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>   <span class=\"p\">};</span></code></pre></div><h3><b>任务2.2.2: 网络传输集成</b></h3><p data-pid=\"RnXKJtFk\"><b>好消息</b>: NCCL的网络层相对独立，如果您的芯片支持标准RDMA，可以直接复用：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"nAA4Bvdt\">InfiniBand支持（<code>src/transport/net_ib.cc</code>）</li><li data-pid=\"zPoeaBDs\">Socket支持（<code>src/transport/net_socket.cc</code>）</li></ul><p data-pid=\"5ctMNJvz\"><b>需要确认的能力</b>:</p><ol><li data-pid=\"AiABPKY6\">GPU-Direct RDMA等价功能</li><li data-pid=\"WKDOHvij\">DMA-Buf支持（Linux内核5.x+）</li><li data-pid=\"v6qn7Qe_\">网卡与芯片的DMA能力</li></ol><h3><b>任务2.2.3: 共享内存传输</b></h3><p data-pid=\"ERo_E_oK\"><b>文件</b>: <code>src/transport/shm.cc</code></p><p data-pid=\"tH8JSwXT\"><b>需要确认</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"Y8TOVk12\">节点内多芯片通过共享内存通信的能力</li><li data-pid=\"wIDJnB-b\"><code>/dev/shm</code>或类似机制的支持</li></ul><h3>2.3 第三阶段：拓扑发现与调度</h3><h3><b>任务2.3.1: 拓扑检测</b></h3><p data-pid=\"KHPvYJ0D\"><b>核心文件</b>: <code>src/graph/topo.cc</code>, <code>src/graph/xml.cc</code></p><p data-pid=\"FU6NzUq5\"><b>需要替换的API</b>:</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"c1\">// NVML API替换（当前在src/init.cc中使用）\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span><span class=\"n\">nvmlDeviceGetHandleByPciBusId</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>     <span class=\"err\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">NPU芯片的管理API</span>\n<span class=\"n\">nvmlDeviceGetIndex</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>                <span class=\"err\">→</span> <span class=\"err\">获取设备索引</span>\n<span class=\"n\">nvmlDeviceGetPciInfo</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>              <span class=\"err\">→</span> <span class=\"err\">获取</span><span class=\"n\">PCIe信息</span>\n<span class=\"n\">nvmlDeviceGetNvLinkCapability</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>     <span class=\"err\">→</span> <span class=\"err\">获取互联能力</span></code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"LK-bNwua\"><b>拓扑信息需求</b>（参考<code>src/graph/topo.h</code>）:</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"n\">ncclTopoNode</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">type</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>        <span class=\"c1\">// GPU/PCI/CPU/NIC/NET\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>  <span class=\"n\">int64_t</span> <span class=\"n\">id</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>      <span class=\"c1\">// 唯一标识\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>  <span class=\"k\">union</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">dev</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>              <span class=\"c1\">// 设备编号\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>      <span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">rank</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>             <span class=\"c1\">// NCCL rank\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>      <span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">cudaCompCap</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>      <span class=\"c1\">// 计算能力（需要定义您芯片的等价物）\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>      <span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">gdrSupport</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>       <span class=\"c1\">// GPU-Direct RDMA支持\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>    <span class=\"p\">}</span> <span class=\"n\">gpu</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"n\">uint64_t</span> <span class=\"n\">asic</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>        <span class=\"c1\">// 网卡ASIC ID\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>      <span class=\"kt\">float</span> <span class=\"n\">bw</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>             <span class=\"c1\">// 带宽\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>      <span class=\"kt\">float</span> <span class=\"n\">latency</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>        <span class=\"c1\">// 延迟\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>      <span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">gdrSupport</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>       <span class=\"c1\">// GDR支持\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>    <span class=\"p\">}</span> <span class=\"n\">net</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"p\">};</span>\n  <span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">nlinks</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"n\">ncclTopoLink</span> <span class=\"n\">links</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">NCCL_TOPO_MAX_LINKS</span><span class=\"p\">];</span>  <span class=\"c1\">// 互联链路\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span><span class=\"p\">};</span></code></pre></div><h3><b>任务2.3.2: 性能建模与调优</b></h3><p data-pid=\"kRjD8rn9\"><b>文件</b>: <code>src/graph/tuning.cc</code></p><p data-pid=\"rhUvbf_V\"><b>需要测量的性能参数</b>:</p><p data-pid=\"cjEh1I_Q\"><b>1，带宽常量</b>（参考<code>src/graph/topo.h</code>）</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"cp\">#define LOC_BW 5000.0           </span><span class=\"c1\">// 本地内存带宽（GB/s）\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span><span class=\"cp\">#define CHIP_NVLINK_BW XX.0     </span><span class=\"c1\">// 您芯片的互联带宽\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span><span class=\"cp\">#define PCI_BW 12.0             </span><span class=\"c1\">// PCIe Gen3 x16\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span><span class=\"cp\">#define NET_BW 12.0             // 网络带宽</span></code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"20sv4R_1\"> 2，<b>延迟测量</b><br/> </p><ul><li data-pid=\"qXg1psOG\"> 芯片内访问延迟</li><li data-pid=\"GIMe0uAa\">芯片间互联延迟</li><li data-pid=\"5aB63oq8\"> 网络延迟<br/> </li></ul><p data-pid=\"-vY8xX49\">3， <b>算法选择策略</b><br/> </p><ul><li data-pid=\"G7Elal33\"> Ring算法：适合带宽受限</li><li data-pid=\"HXukcj-J\">Tree算法：适合延迟敏感</li><li data-pid=\"WM8F_H5s\">Direct算法：适合小规模</li></ul><h3>2.4 第四阶段：内核优化</h3><h3><b>任务2.4.1: 集合算法移植</b></h3><p data-pid=\"WzEOL_G-\"><b>需要移植的算法</b>:</p><p data-pid=\"aiywkO3t\"> 1，<b>AllReduce</b>（<code>src/device/all_reduce.h</code>）</p><ul><li data-pid=\"tDB1l16g\"> Ring AllReduce</li><li data-pid=\"WbGAX1St\">Tree AllReduce</li><li data-pid=\"wI0e6Bix\">CollNet Direct</li><li data-pid=\"YwwHVwA_\"> NVLS (如果有类似硬件加速)</li></ul><p data-pid=\"5keAqiFN\"> 2，<b>AllGather</b>（<code>src/device/all_gather.h</code>）</p><ul><li data-pid=\"kchCrBM0\"> Ring AllGather</li><li data-pid=\"b2NQVf-C\"> Direct AllGather</li></ul><p data-pid=\"0famV32F\">3， <b>ReduceScatter</b>（<code>src/device/reduce_scatter.h</code>）</p><p data-pid=\"-qxQg8oZ\"> 4，<b>Broadcast</b>（<code>src/device/broadcast.h</code>）<br/> </p><p data-pid=\"nI9V7eGD\"><b>优化要点</b>:</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"c1\">// 关键性能参数（src/include/device.h）\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span><span class=\"cp\">#define WARP_SIZE 32                    </span><span class=\"c1\">// 您芯片的Warp大小\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span><span class=\"cp\">#define NCCL_MAX_NTHREADS 640           </span><span class=\"c1\">// 最大线程数\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span><span class=\"cp\">#define NCCL_LL128_LINESIZE 128         </span><span class=\"c1\">// LL128协议行大小\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span><span class=\"cp\">#define NCCL_LL128_SHMEM_SIZE (...)     // 共享内存需求</span></code></pre></div><h3><b>任务2.4.2: Reduction操作</b></h3><p data-pid=\"eVMj4vgw\"><b>文件</b>: <code>src/device/reduce_kernel.h</code></p><p data-pid=\"SAXhYIog\"><b>需要实现的Reduce操作</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"3k6tYpP6\">Sum, Prod, Min, Max</li><li data-pid=\"bxEV4l23\">支持的数据类型: FP32, FP16, BF16, INT32, INT64</li></ul><p data-pid=\"eddGNgkn\"><b>硬件加速机会</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"Z8qsiqbZ\">如果您的芯片有向量/张量单元，可以加速reduction</li><li data-pid=\"ngB83i6z\">利用原子操作硬件</li></ul><h3><b>任务2.4.3: 协议实现</b></h3><p data-pid=\"_7G61MKl\"><b>三种协议的特点</b>:</p><p data-pid=\"zmF9ejkk\"> 1，<b>Simple协议</b>（<code>src/device/prims_simple.h</code>）<br/> </p><ul><li data-pid=\"mPibG_3i\"> 批量传输，适合大消息</li><li data-pid=\"Uyqq1P98\">缓冲区大小：4MB（可调）</li><li data-pid=\"1KCWiCuc\"> 步进式流水线<br/> </li></ul><p data-pid=\"Y4-BvQef\"> 2，<b>LL协议</b>（<code>src/device/prims_ll.h</code>）<br/> </p><ul><li data-pid=\"IrlM9s5y\"> 每个数据包携带flag，低延迟</li><li data-pid=\"tnyyhzt-\">适合小消息(&lt;8KB)</li><li data-pid=\"419yQt1J\"> 需要原子操作支持<br/> </li></ul><p data-pid=\"mywey3OU\"> 3，<b>LL128协议</b>（<code>src/device/prims_ll128.h</code>）<br/> </p><ul><li data-pid=\"TX5UR3zD\"> 128字节行，平衡性能</li><li data-pid=\"fKKByP_f\">适合中等消息</li></ul><h3>2.5 第五阶段：测试与验证</h3><h3><b>任务2.5.1: 功能测试</b></h3><p data-pid=\"RwBdRN_c\"><b>测试范围</b>:</p><ol><li data-pid=\"AfK5y0jF\">单节点、多芯片</li><li data-pid=\"ss5GajQ3\">多节点、多芯片</li><li data-pid=\"WxLeo068\">所有集合操作</li><li data-pid=\"TMWHP1OK\">所有数据类型</li><li data-pid=\"LeNiumc0\">各种消息大小</li></ol><h3><b>任务2.5.2: 性能基准测试</b></h3><p data-pid=\"5OJUN3Wg\"><b>关键指标</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"OmgcHGVE\">算法带宽 (GB/s)</li><li data-pid=\"hq1WB4wN\">延迟 (μs)</li><li data-pid=\"FMQFCRsc\">可扩展性（强扩展、弱扩展）</li></ul><h3>3. AI芯片设计要求</h3><h3>3.1 强制性硬件特性</h3><h3><b>3.1.1 内存子系统</b></h3><table data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"table\" data-size=\"normal\" data-row-style=\"normal\"><tbody><tr><th>特性</th><th>要求</th><th>NCCL依赖原因</th></tr><tr><td>全局内存带宽</td><td>≥1 TB/s</td><td>集合通信吞吐量瓶颈</td></tr><tr><td>共享内存容量</td><td>≥64 KB/计算单元</td><td>NCCL内核缓冲区需求</td></tr><tr><td>共享内存带宽</td><td>≥4 TB/s</td><td>LL128协议性能</td></tr><tr><td>缓存一致性</td><td>硬件支持</td><td>多计算单元协作</td></tr><tr><td>ECC支持</td><td>推荐</td><td>可靠性</td></tr></tbody></table><p data-pid=\"oFGkET6N\"><b>设计建议</b>:</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">推荐内存层次:\nL1 Cache: 128 KB/计算单元（指令+数据）\n共享内存: 64-128 KB/计算单元（可编程管理）\nL2 Cache: 4-8 MB/芯片（所有计算单元共享）\nHBM: 32-80 GB（带宽&gt;1 TB/s）</code></pre></div><h3><b>3.1.2 计算层次结构</b></h3><p data-pid=\"7n6QI1kn\">注： SIMD 芯片缺线程编程模型，需要根据实际情况做调整修改。</p><p data-pid=\"FFxQGRk-\">基于NCCL的线程模型（<code>src/include/device.h:85-92</code>）:</p><table data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"table\" data-size=\"normal\" data-row-style=\"normal\"><tbody><tr><th>NCCL概念</th><th>推荐规格</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td>Thread</td><td>基本计算单元</td><td>标量或SIMD lane</td></tr><tr><td>Warp</td><td>32或64个Thread</td><td>同步执行单元</td></tr><tr><td>Block</td><td>512-1024个Thread</td><td>共享内存作用域</td></tr><tr><td>Grid</td><td>无限制</td><td>任务级并行</td></tr></tbody></table><p data-pid=\"4Mzf_WvL\"><b>关键要求</b>:</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"c1\">// 并发线程数（src/include/device.h）\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span><span class=\"cp\">#define WARP_SIZE 32              </span><span class=\"c1\">// 您可以选择32或64\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span><span class=\"cp\">#define NCCL_MAX_NTHREADS 640     </span><span class=\"c1\">// 每个Block的最大线程数\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span><span class=\"cp\">#define MAXCHANNELS 64            // 最大通道数</span></code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"Q_8DhFQC\"><b>计算能力估算</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"Po9yxRLp\">假设32核心/芯片，每核心支持1024线程</li><li data-pid=\"IudTFzCJ\">总并发线程: 32,768</li><li data-pid=\"zy5ICEGd\">适合运行64个NCCL通道（每通道512线程）</li></ul><h3><b>3.1.3 同步与原子操作</b></h3><p data-pid=\"MkVTaOWr\">注： SIMD 芯片缺同步与原子编程模型的话，需要根据实际情况做调整修改。</p><p data-pid=\"LhNHyPja\"><b>必须支持的原语</b>（基于<code>src/device/common.h</code>）:</p><p data-pid=\"t7pwMMWe\"><b>1，Barrier同步</b></p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"c1\">// 命名Barrier（支持多达16个独立Barrier）\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>   <span class=\"n\">barrier_sync</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">barrier_id</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">thread_count</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n\n   <span class=\"c1\">// Barrier with reduction\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>   <span class=\"n\">barrier_red_or</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">vote</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">barrier_id</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">thread_count</span><span class=\"p\">);</span></code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"0KvmDxTF\"><b>2，原子操作</b></p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"c1\">// 内存作用域的原子操作\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>   <span class=\"n\">atomicAdd</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">addr</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">value</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>      <span class=\"c1\">// 原子加\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>   <span class=\"n\">atomicCAS</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">addr</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">cmp</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">value</span><span class=\"p\">);</span> <span class=\"c1\">// 比较并交换\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>   <span class=\"n\">atomicMin</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">Max</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">addr</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">value</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>  <span class=\"c1\">// 原子最小/最大\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>\n   <span class=\"c1\">// 需要支持的数据类型\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>   <span class=\"o\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">int32_t</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">uint32_t</span>\n   <span class=\"o\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">int64_t</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">uint64_t</span>\n   <span class=\"o\">-</span> <span class=\"kt\">float</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"err\">可选但推荐</span><span class=\"p\">)</span></code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"M3IGdYxE\"><b>3，内存栅栏</b></p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"n\">__threadfence</span><span class=\"p\">();</span>         <span class=\"c1\">// 线程级栅栏\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>   <span class=\"n\">__threadfence_block</span><span class=\"p\">();</span>   <span class=\"c1\">// Block级栅栏\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span>   <span class=\"n\">__threadfence_system</span><span class=\"p\">();</span>  <span class=\"o\">//</span> <span class=\"err\">系统级栅栏（跨芯片）</span></code></pre></div><h3><b>3.1.4 互联架构</b></h3><p data-pid=\"gee6lzsD\"><b>节点内互联</b>（芯片间）:</p><table data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"table\" data-size=\"normal\" data-row-style=\"normal\"><tbody><tr><th>互联类型</th><th>带宽要求</th><th>延迟要求</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td>芯片直连</td><td>≥200 GB/s双向</td><td>&lt;500 ns</td><td>类似NVLink</td></tr><tr><td>PCIe</td><td>Gen4 x16以上</td><td>&lt;2 μs</td><td>备用通道</td></tr><tr><td>共享内存总线</td><td>≥100 GB/s</td><td>&lt;100 ns</td><td>同NUMA节点</td></tr></tbody></table><p data-pid=\"tM3_2EKf\"><b>节点间互联</b>:</p><table data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"table\" data-size=\"normal\" data-row-style=\"normal\"><tbody><tr><th>互联类型</th><th>带宽要求</th><th>延迟要求</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td>RDMA网络</td><td>100-400 Gbps</td><td>&lt;5 μs</td><td>InfiniBand/RoCEv2</td></tr><tr><td>GPU-Direct RDMA</td><td>必须支持</td><td>-</td><td>零拷贝网络传输</td></tr></tbody></table><p data-pid=\"mE2M4lr-\"><b>拓扑建议</b>:</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">单节点8芯片配置:\n- 芯片0-3通过高速互联环形连接\n- 芯片4-7通过高速互联环形连接\n- 两个环之间通过桥接芯片互联\n- 每个芯片独立的PCIe x16连接\n- 2-4个RDMA网卡，均匀分布</code></pre></div><h3>3.2 高度推荐的特性</h3><h3><b>3.2.1 直接内存访问（DMA）</b></h3><p data-pid=\"oHu3LrJ1\"><b>GPU-Direct RDMA等价物</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"PtHUoAFB\">网卡直接访问芯片内存，无需CPU参与</li><li data-pid=\"jfp1_x5t\">支持注册内存区域（Memory Registration）</li><li data-pid=\"la5TXn5W\">DMA引擎支持异步数据搬移</li></ul><p data-pid=\"fm7rsxDY\"><b>实现要点</b>（参考<code>src/transport/net.cc</code>）:</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"c1\">// 内存注册接口\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span><span class=\"n\">ncclResult_t</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">regMr</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">comm</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">data</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">size_t</span> <span class=\"n\">size</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> \n                      <span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">type</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">**</span> <span class=\"n\">mhandle</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">// 直接发送/接收\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span><span class=\"n\">ncclResult_t</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">isend</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">sendComm</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">data</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">size_t</span> <span class=\"n\">size</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> \n                      <span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">tag</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">mhandle</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">**</span> <span class=\"n\">request</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"n\">ncclResult_t</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">irecv</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">recvComm</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">data</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">size_t</span> <span class=\"n\">size</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> \n                      <span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">tag</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">mhandle</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"o\">**</span> <span class=\"n\">request</span><span class=\"p\">);</span></code></pre></div><h3><b>3.2.2 虚拟化与多流支持</b></h3><p data-pid=\"VV3oKqMp\"><b>流（Stream）管理</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"tCN_E_sH\">独立的命令队列（建议≥32个/芯片）</li><li data-pid=\"aM4iU_ba\">异步执行支持</li><li data-pid=\"2CmzeePG\">流间依赖关系管理</li></ul><p data-pid=\"dO60tje7\"><b>优先级调度</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"jqCpkPAL\">支持高/低优先级流</li><li data-pid=\"YaDCcMNL\">抢占机制（用于低延迟任务）</li></ul><h3><b>3.2.3 调试与性能分析</b></h3><p data-pid=\"lS-LVXkK\"><b>硬件性能计数器</b>:</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"c1\">// 建议的计数器\n</span><span class=\"c1\"></span><span class=\"o\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">Memory</span> <span class=\"n\">bandwidth</span> <span class=\"n\">utilization</span>\n<span class=\"o\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">Compute</span> <span class=\"n\">unit</span> <span class=\"n\">utilization</span>\n<span class=\"o\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">Interconnect</span> <span class=\"n\">utilization</span>\n<span class=\"o\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">Stall</span> <span class=\"n\">cycles</span> <span class=\"n\">by</span> <span class=\"n\">reason</span>\n<span class=\"o\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">Cache</span> <span class=\"n\">hit</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">miss</span> <span class=\"n\">rates</span></code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"EBmrVby4\"><b>Trace支持</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"tTTFUgcz\">内核启动/完成时间戳</li><li data-pid=\"AOFZesfG\">内存传输trace</li><li data-pid=\"AFRDQ7E1\">互联通信trace</li></ul><h3>3.3 性能目标</h3><p data-pid=\"pCXPzScB\">基于NCCL在NVIDIA GPU上的表现，NPU芯片应达到：</p><table data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"table\" data-size=\"normal\" data-row-style=\"normal\"><tbody><tr><th>操作</th><th>消息大小</th><th>目标带宽</th><th>目标延迟</th></tr><tr><td>AllReduce</td><td>8 MB</td><td>≥80%峰值带宽</td><td>&lt;100 μs基础延迟</td></tr><tr><td>AllReduce</td><td>128 B</td><td>-</td><td>&lt;20 μs</td></tr><tr><td>AllGather</td><td>8 MB</td><td>≥90%峰值带宽</td><td>&lt;80 μs</td></tr><tr><td>Broadcast</td><td>8 MB</td><td>≥85%峰值带宽</td><td>&lt;60 μs</td></tr></tbody></table><p data-pid=\"-uNAob8_\"><b>多节点扩展</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"3XbXFjug\">2节点效率: &gt;95%</li><li data-pid=\"QTCyK3wh\">4节点效率: &gt;92%</li><li data-pid=\"PrHAsz_0\">8节点效率: &gt;90%</li></ul><h3>4. 关键技术决策</h3><h3>4.1 编程模型选择</h3><h3><b>选项A: CUDA兼容模型</b></h3><p data-pid=\"SwjLaOoy\"><b>优点</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"RCfj4cW3\">最小化移植工作</li><li data-pid=\"xP8Z_tzp\">利用现有CUDA生态系统</li><li data-pid=\"X2zs3gd7\">开发人员熟悉</li></ul><p data-pid=\"2r3M4vB6\"><b>缺点</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"tJrsca5F\">可能无法充分发挥硬件特性</li><li data-pid=\"Mjf0HhEa\">受限于CUDA语义</li></ul><p data-pid=\"3M0xvV4A\"><b>推荐度</b>: 5星， 如果目标是快速完成支持</p><h3><b>选项B: SYCL/OpenCL模型</b></h3><p data-pid=\"h8GMCLpm\"><b>优点</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"O0oD-UDm\">标准化、跨平台</li><li data-pid=\"Q_TBQHI_\">工具链成熟</li></ul><p data-pid=\"azHqEthA\"><b>缺点</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"TZ5q4PHA\">性能可能不如CUDA</li><li data-pid=\"yAF4gKfp\">需要重写内核</li></ul><p data-pid=\"JaqSQxC7\"><b>推荐度</b>: 3星，如果追求开放标准</p><h3><b>选项C: 定制DSL</b></h3><p data-pid=\"sjW0G__N\"><b>优点</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"yjq2bDmf\">完全定制化，最优性能</li><li data-pid=\"etM5k8gL\">可以引入领域特定优化</li></ul><p data-pid=\"h4a1Rr2G\"><b>缺点</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"hNa7WpqA\">学习曲线陡峭</li><li data-pid=\"cAor3bld\">生态系统从零开始</li></ul><p data-pid=\"W5iNSkSz\"><b>推荐度</b>: 2星，仅当有独特架构优势时考虑</p><h3>4.2 互联架构决策</h3><h3><b>选项A: 纯PCIe方案</b></h3><p data-pid=\"ZgdB7lzJ\"><b>规格</b>: PCIe Gen5 x16 (64 GB/s双向)</p><p data-pid=\"YlyEsi26\"><b>优点</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"6LtW1DL0\">成本低</li><li data-pid=\"URL2bT4T\">生态成熟</li></ul><p data-pid=\"EP4oayAY\"><b>缺点</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"Itr1NOWK\">带宽受限</li><li data-pid=\"CERMJzDd\">延迟较高(~2-5μs)</li></ul><p data-pid=\"3-RtktYh\"><b>适用场景</b>: 入门级产品</p><h3><b>选项B: 自研高速互联</b></h3><p data-pid=\"d4SYruoP\"><b>规格</b>: 200-400 GB/s双向，&lt;500ns延迟</p><p data-pid=\"zI1Tv7_4\"><b>优点</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"az8kx13a\">高性能</li><li data-pid=\"Km06Et35\">可定制拓扑</li></ul><p data-pid=\"g4Z58NrQ\"><b>缺点</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"PMOrCocd\">研发成本高</li><li data-pid=\"4PgS87AP\">生态封闭</li></ul><p data-pid=\"UwVh17a3\"><b>适用场景</b>: 高端数据中心产品</p><h3><b>选项C: 混合方案（推荐）</b></h3><p data-pid=\"hhzoKw9B\"><b>规格</b>: 高速互联 + PCIe</p><p data-pid=\"O6F64vx2\"><b>优点</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"bUWhlcE_\">性能与兼容性兼顾</li><li data-pid=\"yXQDbB6j\">灵活的拓扑选择</li></ul><p data-pid=\"og_7zSa-\"><b>缺点</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"1QYqS-GA\">复杂度较高</li></ul><p data-pid=\"ngTu4YXl\"><b>推荐度</b>: 5星</p><h3>4.3 内存模型决策</h3><h3><b>选项A: 统一内存（Unified Memory）</b></h3><p data-pid=\"VJGM6mIy\"><b>优点</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"pKjdNdku\">编程简单</li><li data-pid=\"629t2pJt\">减少显式数据传输</li></ul><p data-pid=\"wE-2d4PC\"><b>缺点</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"wM6jddGZ\">性能可能损失10-30%</li><li data-pid=\"k7QCphzP\">页面迁移开销</li></ul><p data-pid=\"UHMdSyDG\"><b>推荐</b>: 作为可选特性提供</p><h3><b>选项B: 显式内存管理（推荐）</b></h3><p data-pid=\"c0IUsGKD\"><b>优点</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"_CQGfTPr\">最优性能</li><li data-pid=\"QrzIpWFn\">程序员完全控制</li></ul><p data-pid=\"b1Ty0JST\"><b>缺点</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"xm11ryZW\">编程复杂度高</li></ul><p data-pid=\"uIi_yX0r\"><b>推荐度</b>: 5星， 作为默认模式</p><h3>5. 风险评估</h3><h3>5.1 高风险项</h3><table data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"table\" data-size=\"normal\" data-row-style=\"normal\"><tbody><tr><th>风险项</th><th>风险等级</th><th>影响</th><th>缓解措施</th></tr><tr><td>内核语言兼容性</td><td>极高</td><td>移植时间×2</td><td>早期投入编译器/工具链</td></tr><tr><td>芯片间互联性能</td><td>高</td><td>无法达到性能目标</td><td>硬件设计阶段充分验证</td></tr><tr><td>拓扑发现API</td><td>中</td><td>调试困难</td><td>设计完善的管理API</td></tr><tr><td>RDMA集成</td><td>中</td><td>网络性能受限</td><td>与网卡厂商早期合作</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>5.2 中风险项</h3><table data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"table\" data-size=\"normal\" data-row-style=\"normal\"><tbody><tr><th>风险项</th><th>风险等级</th><th>影响</th><th>缓解措施</th></tr><tr><td>多节点扩展性</td><td>中</td><td>大规模训练受限</td><td>充分的性能测试</td></tr><tr><td>生态集成</td><td>中</td><td>用户采用困难</td><td>提供完善的文档和示例</td></tr><tr><td>调试工具</td><td>低</td><td>开发效率降低</td><td>开发专用调试工具</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>5.3 技术债务风险</h3><p data-pid=\"6YuqOsq8\"><b>警告</b>: 如果为了快速完成交付，跳过以下工作，将积累技术债务：</p><ol><li data-pid=\"XoV_mW6j\">性能调优不充分 → 用户投诉，市场口碑差</li><li data-pid=\"ldt2fdvZ\">测试覆盖不足 → 线上故障，可靠性问题</li><li data-pid=\"GEMbLHSx\">文档不完善 → 用户使用困难，支持成本高</li><li data-pid=\"spLMPMI4\">API设计不合理 → 后续版本兼容性问题</li></ol><h3>6. 实施建议</h3><h3>6.1 渐进式移植策略</h3><p data-pid=\"DWeOc51T\"><b>第1步：概念验证</b></p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">目标：单节点、单芯片、AllReduce算法\n范围：\n  - 最小HAL层实现\n  - Simple协议移植\n  - Ring AllReduce算法\n  - 基础测试框架\n验收标准：\n  - 功能正确性：100%通过单元测试\n  - 性能：达到理论带宽的60%</code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"FcwVx77t\"><b>第2步：多卡支持</b></p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">目标：单节点、多卡、主要集合操作\n范围：\n  - P2P传输层\n  - 拓扑发现\n  - 所有集合算法（AllReduce, AllGather, ReduceScatter, Broadcast）\n  - LL协议支持\n验收标准：\n  - 8芯片线性扩展效率&gt;85%\n  - 支持所有数据类型</code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"UO-6mwXL\"><b>第3步：多节点支持</b></p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">目标：多节点、多卡、生产可用\n范围：\n  - 网络传输层优化\n  - LL128协议\n  - RDMA支持\n  - 性能调优\n验收标准：\n  - 4节点扩展效率&gt;80%\n  - AllReduce吞吐量达到理论峰值的85%</code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"FB2NnVil\"><b>第4步：生产加固</b></p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">目标：企业级可靠性、性能优化\n范围：\n  - 容错机制\n  - 调试工具\n  - 性能分析工具\n  - 文档完善\n验收标准：\n  - 通过1000小时稳定性测试\n  - 完整的用户文档</code></pre></div><h3>6.2 质量保证</h3><p data-pid=\"CiTZXr1M\"><b>代码质量</b>:</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"c1\"># 自动化检查</span>\n- 静态分析：Coverity, cppcheck\n- 代码覆盖率：&gt;80%\n- 单元测试：&gt;90%功能覆盖\n- 集成测试：主要场景100%覆盖</code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"iVW5wPPl\"><b>性能基准</b>:</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"c1\"># 每次提交自动运行</span>\n1. AllReduce性能（各种消息大小）\n2. AllGather性能\n3. 多节点扩展性\n4. 延迟测试\n5. 吞吐量测试\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># 回归阈值</span>\n- 性能下降&gt;5%则失败\n- 功能测试失败则阻止合入</code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"hJiUUX2i\"><b>文档要求</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"qJbDLQHe\">API文档100%覆盖</li><li data-pid=\"CZm26i2a\">用户指南（安装、配置、调优）</li><li data-pid=\"e_cmu8BP\">故障排查指南</li><li data-pid=\"o-s_TLiV\">性能调优指南</li></ul><h3>7. 成功案例参考</h3><h3>7.1 AMD ROCm移植RCCL</h3><p data-pid=\"LhbCM49V\"><b>背景</b>: AMD将NCCL移植到ROCm平台（RCCL）</p><p data-pid=\"RSitHLh5\"><b>关键决策</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"fMgYFR_Z\">保持NCCL API兼容</li><li data-pid=\"aD0s2zsp\">HIP语言（CUDA兼容层）</li><li data-pid=\"coMwQYE2\">开源社区驱动</li></ul><p data-pid=\"sZkBEnew\"><b>结果</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"3MPU8xSH\">功能：100% NCCL兼容</li><li data-pid=\"I7kpdQxN\">性能：80-95% NVIDIA性能</li><li data-pid=\"xtdqCWJB\">时间：约3个月达到生产可用</li></ul><p data-pid=\"djAewVkJ\"><b>启示</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"pEVleQOn\">API兼容性至关重要</li><li data-pid=\"NbZatxOP\">性能优化是长期过程</li><li data-pid=\"9tTnZKjf\">社区支持加速采用</li></ul><h3>7.2 Graphcore IPU通信库</h3><p data-pid=\"xqhAs9AT\"><b>背景</b>: Graphcore为IPU架构设计通信库</p><p data-pid=\"k2K7G-0d\"><b>关键决策</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"G2JY-Lx-\">定制化设计（针对IPU特性）</li><li data-pid=\"vhoMBamx\">集成到Poplar SDK</li><li data-pid=\"HE5w7-aB\">不兼容NCCL API</li></ul><p data-pid=\"fLqXDMGO\"><b>结果</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"tTpknIgc\">功能：针对IPU优化</li><li data-pid=\"0AadM2k9\">性能：特定workload优异</li><li data-pid=\"VJBlhAXy\">生态：学习曲线陡峭</li></ul><p data-pid=\"ONghZwNw\"><b>启示</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"VnXZB9w-\">定制化可获得更好性能</li><li data-pid=\"RgN-8OtI\">但牺牲了生态兼容性</li></ul><h3>8. 总结与建议</h3><p data-pid=\"aq7Sc50o\"><b>1，优先级排序</b></p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">P0（必须）: CUDA Runtime API抽象层\n   P0（必须）: 单节点AllReduce（Ring算法）\n   P1（重要）: 多芯片P2P传输\n   P1（重要）: 所有集合操作\n   P2（增强）: LL/LL128协议\n   P3（优化）: 高级拓扑优化</code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"W3Ud8lCE\"> 2，<b>技术路线</b><br/> </p><ul><li data-pid=\"QuUgwKZB\"> 推荐: CUDA兼容编程模型 + 混合互联 + 显式内存管理</li><li data-pid=\"vTSVQaDg\"> 避免: 过早优化、忽视测试、文档不足</li><li data-pid=\"jiTZ0qDC\"> 硬件要求优先级</li></ul><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">关键：\n   - 高带宽内存（&gt;1 TB/s）\n   - 硬件barrier支持\n   - 原子操作\n\n   重要：\n   - 芯片间高速互联（&gt;200 GB/s）\n   - GPU-Direct RDMA\n\n   增强：\n   - 硬件性能计数器\n   - Trace功能</code></pre></div><h3>附录</h3><h3>A. 关键文件清单</h3><p data-pid=\"M2g54aw6\"><b>必读源码</b>（按优先级）:</p><ol><li data-pid=\"9lAN4YCo\"><code>src/include/device.h</code> - 设备抽象接口</li><li data-pid=\"fIOJAS33\"><code>src/include/nccl.h</code> - 公共API定义</li><li data-pid=\"lYn2JoVe\"><code>src/device/common.h</code> - 设备端通用头文件</li><li data-pid=\"0dmNRt3C\"><code>src/device/primitives.h</code> - 通信原语</li><li data-pid=\"E_UV7nCC\"><code>src/transport/p2p.cc</code> - P2P传输实现</li><li data-pid=\"Ta4BtN1d\"><code>src/graph/topo.cc</code> - 拓扑发现</li><li data-pid=\"oudB2iwR\"><code>src/init.cc</code> - 初始化流程</li></ol><p data-pid=\"2n6DV6ms\"><b>关键算法</b>:</p><ol><li data-pid=\"0Xwl0iOF\"><code>src/device/all_reduce.h</code> - AllReduce实现</li><li data-pid=\"XpvoJEf8\"><code>src/device/reduce_kernel.h</code> - Reduction内核</li><li data-pid=\"vlbpnLnw\"><code>src/device/prims_simple.h</code> - Simple协议</li></ol><h3>B. 性能调优参数</h3><p data-pid=\"zeY3Q8YN\"><b>环境变量</b>（参考<code>src/init.cc</code>）:</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"c1\"># 通道数量</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">NCCL_NCHANNELS</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">32</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># 协议选择</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">NCCL_PROTO</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>Simple  <span class=\"c1\"># 或LL, LL128</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># 缓冲区大小</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">NCCL_BUFFSIZE</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">4194304</span>  <span class=\"c1\"># 4MB</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># P2P阈值</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">NCCL_P2P_LEVEL</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>NVL  <span class=\"c1\"># 或PXB, PHB</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># 调试级别</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">NCCL_DEBUG</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>INFO\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># 拓扑文件</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">NCCL_TOPO_FILE</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>/path/to/topology.xml</code></pre></div><h3>C. 参考资源</h3><p data-pid=\"SPuFP4gV\"><b>官方文档</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"UP9D4HPH\">NCCL Developer Guide: <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//docs.nvidia.com/deeplearning/nccl/\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">docs.nvidia.com/deeplea</span><span class=\"invisible\">rning/nccl/</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></li><li data-pid=\"_Eao3skT\">NCCL GitHub: <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//github.com/NVIDIA/nccl\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">github.com/NVIDIA/nccl</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a></li></ul><p data-pid=\"BGQHLY5I\"><b>论文</b>:</p><ol><li data-pid=\"XzdUpu_x\">&#34;Massively Parallel Deep Learning&#34; (NVIDIA, 2017)</li><li data-pid=\"_4LCIj2n\">&#34;Scaling Distributed Machine Learning with NCCL&#34; (NVIDIA, 2020)</li></ol><p data-pid=\"FY58UQdR\"><b>开源实现参考</b>:</p><ul><li data-pid=\"CKd_Ax7o\">RCCL (AMD): <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//github.com/ROCmSoftwarePlatform/rccl\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">github.com/ROCmSoftware</span><span class=\"invisible\">Platform/rccl</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></li><li data-pid=\"9DlprrBW\">OneCCL (Intel): <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//github.com/oneapi-src/oneCCL\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">github.com/oneapi-src/o</span><span class=\"invisible\">neCCL</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></li></ul><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><h3>版权申明</h3><p data-pid=\"Boj_Pd0x\">本文的版权协议为 CC-BY-NC-ND license：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/3.0/deed.zh\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">creativecommons.org/lic</span><span class=\"invisible\">enses/by-nc-nd/3.0/deed.zh</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></p><p data-pid=\"NyAYuiDH\">在遵循署名、非商业使用（以获利为准）以及禁止演绎的前提下可以自由阅读、分享、转发、复制、分发等。</p>","state":"published","content_need_truncated":true,"image_url":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-0e2662d69e59d31913d175a8b2600136_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b","title":"第16篇 - 集合通信 - 国产AI芯片构建集合通信库的工作分析与建议","can_comment":{"status":true,"reason":"请输入评论，您的评论将会由作者筛选后显示"},"type":"article","suggest_edit":{"status":false,"url":"","reason":"","tip":"","title":""}}
